      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、優\n今、少し時間をもらってもいいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ Yu.\nCan I have a moment of your time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です\nもちろんええで。お仕事のことですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ good work.\nOf course. Is it about work?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、優に新しく広告動画のオファーがきたんだ\n家族旅行の魅力を伝える、ドラマ仕立ての動画らしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ you have received a new offer for an advertising video.\nIt's apparently a drama-style video promoting the appeal of family trips.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.5000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "先日の舞台で優の演技を観て\nぜひ優に出演をと、先方が強く希望しているんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After seeing Yu's acting in the recent stage play‚\nthey strongly want you to appear in it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.0333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふ……よぉ分かってはるなぁ～\nうちの新たな魅力に、早速魅せられてもうたんやね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufufu… they really get it~\nThey've already been captivated by my new charm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（確かにいい演技だったが、苦労したって聞いてるぞ）\n（……なんて突っ込むのは、さすがに野暮だな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Her acting was certainly good‚ but I heard she struggled.）\n（…but pointing that out would be tactless.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.8666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "……？　{user}さん\n何か言いたそうな顔してませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…? {user}-san‚\nyou look like you want to say something.",
        "id": ""
      },
